gHSQC_d2:            Setup parameters for N15 gHSQC pulse sequence
			using decoupler 2  (M)

        syntex:         gHSQC_d2(<'GLIDE'>)
        Description:    Converts the current parameter set to
                        gHSQC experiment for N15 with decoupler 2
                        for N15.  If the argument GLIDE
                        is supplied, PROTON parameter set for that
                        particular sample is first retrived.
        Related:	gHSQC
        		gHSQC15
        
